results.name: Number of connected numbers (A029827) in the interval [2^(n-1)+1, 2^n].
example: From the 64 numbers with ceiling(log_2(x)) = 7, the following 8 are composite connected numbers: 85, 95, 99, 111, 115, 117, 119, 123. Among the others 13 primes, 4 true prime powers and 39 split numbers can be found.
results.author: _Labos Elemer_
